// about section starts
section#about.about
  h2.heading
    i.fas.fa-info-circle
    |  About 
    span RoeRide
  .row
    .image
      img.tilt(src='images/about.png', alt='image')
    .content
      h3 About RoeRide
      p
        | RoeRide is a ride-sharing platform designed to facilitate transportation among students of Roehampton University. Our goal is to provide an affordable, sustainable, and convenient way for students to commute to and from campus. By connecting users traveling in the same direction, RoeRide helps students save money, reduce traffic congestion, and lower their carbon footprint.
        br
        br
        | We understand that commuting can be a hassle, especially for students. That&apos;s why we offer a seamless experience from finding a ride to reaching your destination. Our platform ensures safety and reliability with user ratings and reviews, making your journey stress-free.
        br
        br
        | Join us in making commuting easier, cheaper, and greener for everyone at Roehampton University.
// about section ends
// Features section starts
